          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Parking</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            It is best to park on the opposite side of the road from the cottage, but not in the church drive. If there is no space we suggest unloading your car outside the cottage then parking it a little way up the hill opposite the village hall.
