          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We welcome dogs but ask that they are kept downstairs and that you use the stair gate provided to ensure we keep the upstairs rooms animal free. We have provided a dog towel, bed and bowl so that your four-legged friend is as well catered for as we hope you are.
          </p>
