      <!-- Local Walks -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-8">Local Walks</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Lambley Viaduct</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              A must-see while staying at the Old Cottage, and it is only a five minute walk away. Start by going up the hill and turn left at the sign posted path at the top of the hill. Follow the path down and cross the old railway line.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">The South Tyne Trail</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Walking north: From the four-way signpost below the Lambley Viaduct turn right to climb up onto the viaduct, then follow the old railway line as far as you want.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Local Services -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-8">Local Services</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-6">Medical Services</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li>
                <strong class="block">Local Doctor</strong>
                <p>Haltwhistle Medical Group<br/>01434320077</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="block">Local Dentist</strong>
                <p>Haltwhistle Dental Health<br/>01434322300</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="block">Emergency A&E</strong>
                <p>Cumberland Infirmary, Carlisle</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-6">Local Transport</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li>
                <strong class="block">Local Taxi</strong>
                <p>Sproul Taxis: 07712321064</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="block">Bus Service</strong>
                <p>Bus 681 from Lambley to Haltwhistle or Alston (3 or 4 times a day)</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Health and Safety -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-6">Health & Safety</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>• No smoking or candles in the house</li>
          <li>• Fire exits via front and back doors (thumb turn locks)</li>
          <li>• Torches provided in bedside units</li>
          <li>• Fire blanket in kitchen</li>
          <li>• First aid kit in top cupboard left of cooker</li>
          <li>• Defibrillator at village hall (2 minutes away)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
